WEBVTT

00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:02.040
ke- GERTNER.

00:00:03.083 --> 00:00:04.764
nu, kh'ken dertseyln?

00:00:05.698 --> 00:00:09.269
az mir zaynen geven, ⟨hot men dos⟩, az mir zaynen geven in RUSSENSCHIN

00:00:05.930 --> 00:00:07.030
du g-

00:00:09.462 --> 00:00:10.564
eyn mol

00:00:10.564 --> 00:00:12.746
zaynen mir gekumen fun der arbet

00:00:13.427 --> 00:00:15.395
farmaterte

00:00:16.043 --> 00:00:17.792
hungerike

00:00:18.068 --> 00:00:21.403
hot di lager firer, di, di mh, di kapo

00:00:21.409 --> 00:00:22.739
di AUFSEHERIN

00:00:22.739 --> 00:00:23.970
gefunen

00:00:23.970 --> 00:00:26.836
shtroy oysgeshotn oyfn, oyfn

00:00:26.860 --> 00:00:27.984
oyf, in hoyf

00:00:28.564 --> 00:00:31.460
hot zi gemakht a tuml, "ver hot dos gemakht?"

00:00:32.006 --> 00:00:34.988
⟨az⟩ mir zaynen gekumen fun der arbet, vos veysn mir?

00:00:34.993 --> 00:00:39.513
di vos zaynen geven in lager, ale hobn geshvign, keyner hot keyn vort nit oysgeredt

00:00:39.513 --> 00:00:40.843
ver s'hot gemakht.

00:00:40.950 --> 00:00:43.087
hot zi undz gegebn a shtrof

00:00:43.819 --> 00:00:45.973
mir zoln z- oyf di kni

00:00:46.047 --> 00:00:47.779
di hent in di heykh

00:00:48.190 --> 00:00:51.958
un untn oyf di kni iz geven shteyndelekh azelkhene

00:00:51.958 --> 00:00:54.225
hobn mir gedarft a halb sho

00:00:54.754 --> 00:00:56.452
shteyn oyf di kni

00:00:56.560 --> 00:00:59.530
un di hent in di heykh, un zi iz arumgelofn

00:00:59.530 --> 00:01:01.400
"HANDE HOCH, HANDE HOCH"

00:01:01.408 --> 00:01:03.387
m'hot gedarft haltn di hent in di heykh

00:01:04.693 --> 00:01:07.740
un di vayber hobn gezogt, ot di vos zey veysn, zogn zey

00:01:07.740 --> 00:01:08.560
az dos iz

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:10.810
d- haynt iz haynt erev yomkiper.

00:01:14.008 --> 00:01:14.795
ye.

00:01:16.489 --> 00:01:19.807
dos iz geven in di lagern, iz geven

00:01:22.294 --> 00:01:23.891
a sakh tsu reydn.

00:01:25.470 --> 00:01:27.730
ikh fil fregn a, a SHEELA

00:01:25.550 --> 00:01:27.550
un u- un di

00:01:28.170 --> 00:01:29.280
tsi

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:31.500
haynt, oyf di letste yorn

00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:34.500
du gedenkst nokh ales vos iz geven, di

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:36.109
di kholems fun dem?

00:01:36.553 --> 00:01:37.740
ale f-

00:01:37.740 --> 00:01:39.132
UNK nokh ⟨vi⟩

00:01:39.132 --> 00:01:42.808
far di oygn shteyt mir altskesding. az ikh dertseyl

00:01:44.063 --> 00:01:46.183
ze ikh dos far mayne oygn.

00:01:47.370 --> 00:01:49.895
ikh ze EREDA. ikh ze RUSSESCHIN

00:01:50.037 --> 00:01:53.169
ikh z- ikh ze, alts ze ikh far mayne oygn.

00:01:55.032 --> 00:01:56.781
az me ken nit fargesn.

00:01:59.588 --> 00:02:03.277
vi ken men fargesn az me hot azelkhene iberlebenishn?

00:02:03.283 --> 00:02:04.762
vi ken men fargesn?

00:02:06.355 --> 00:02:08.897
vi ken men fargesn aza min fal

00:02:08.987 --> 00:02:13.228
az m'hot tsugenumen d- dem, di kinder hot men zeyer holt gehat di shvester's

00:02:13.228 --> 00:02:13.874
ye

00:02:14.202 --> 00:02:18.010
az m'hot tsugenumen di kinder, aroysgerisn fun di shvester's hant

00:02:19.078 --> 00:02:21.353
az der himl holt zikh gedarft shpaltn.

00:02:21.353 --> 00:02:23.325
di kinder hobn geveynt

00:02:23.601 --> 00:02:26.717
mener bazunder, vayber bazunder

00:02:26.993 --> 00:02:29.332
tshemodanes iz geven oyf

00:02:29.541 --> 00:02:36.302
bi- b- biz oybn ongevorfn mit tshemodanes. tsugenumen fun mir dem tshemodan. ikh bin geblibn a nakete.

00:02:36.949 --> 00:02:37.786
ye?

00:02:37.962 --> 00:02:39.812
vi ken men dos fargesn?

00:02:40.841 --> 00:02:43.611
di, di may- di ale SIPURIM vos

00:02:43.611 --> 00:02:45.261
host bos- farsteylt di kinder?

00:02:45.261 --> 00:02:47.561
dayne kinder, di zin? beyde zin?

00:02:47.391 --> 00:02:49.514
ale veysn zey. ikh dertseyl.

00:02:50.220 --> 00:02:52.200
az zenen geven in, in shtub

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:53.510
hostu dertseylt?

00:02:53.365 --> 00:02:54.662
ye, ikh dertseyl.

00:02:54.786 --> 00:02:55.559
ye.

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.940
zey visn ales?

00:02:57.064 --> 00:02:59.704
kh'veys nit tsi zey veysn ales, ober zey veysn.

00:02:59.704 --> 00:03:01.534
zey veysn a sakh ikh rey-

00:03:01.553 --> 00:03:04.359
ikh ken nit fargesn. vi ken ikh dos fargesn?

00:03:04.359 --> 00:03:05.563
vi ken men

00:03:04.742 --> 00:03:06.626
ale mol hostu geredt fun dem?

00:03:06.345 --> 00:03:09.376
kh'reyd ale mol. biz haynt tsum tog reyd ikh.

00:03:10.648 --> 00:03:12.414
biz haynt tsum tog reyd ikh.

00:03:16.504 --> 00:03:18.354
vi ken men fargesn dos?

00:03:19.272 --> 00:03:20.531
un in geto

00:03:20.588 --> 00:03:23.012
in geto, ikh fleg geyn oy- oyfn erodrom

00:03:23.220 --> 00:03:24.446
kalt

00:03:24.570 --> 00:03:27.196
kumstu geyn, a hungerike

00:03:27.253 --> 00:03:30.639
a nase. oyf morgn in di fri darfstu vider geyn

00:03:30.848 --> 00:03:37.271
in d- a brigade, geven andere vos hobn gehat brigades UNK vos hostu gedarft hobn bakantshaft.

00:03:37.463 --> 00:03:39.442
s'iz geven an arbets amt.

00:03:39.442 --> 00:03:41.290
in arbets amt hobn gearbet

00:03:41.290 --> 00:03:43.700
di besere mentshn, ye

00:03:43.791 --> 00:03:46.940
di besere mentshn hobn besere bakantshaft

00:03:47.318 --> 00:03:48.459
git men

00:03:48.988 --> 00:03:52.002
makht men a besern pekl. darf makhn a pekl.

00:03:52.245 --> 00:03:53.583
vos iz der pekl?

00:03:53.583 --> 00:03:57.364
me nemt di zakhn, di beste zakhn vos du host, un me gist avekgebn far

00:03:57.364 --> 00:03:59.091
far, far gornisht.

00:03:59.755 --> 00:04:03.455
ikh gedenk eyn mol, di ershte tsayt nokh, hot men gekent a bisl

00:04:03.455 --> 00:04:04.574
baym toyer

00:04:04.783 --> 00:04:05.907
baym tsoym

00:04:06.572 --> 00:04:07.983
vos iz fartsoymt

00:04:08.007 --> 00:04:11.370
flegn, dortn, ⟨un⟩ di litviner hobn gehit

00:04:11.370 --> 00:04:13.000
iz di litviner

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:15.930
flegn unterkoyfn dem, dem hiter

00:04:15.930 --> 00:04:17.540
flegt er zikh avekgeyn

00:04:17.540 --> 00:04:19.160
un do flegn zey handlen.

00:04:19.464 --> 00:04:23.123
zogt zi, zogt mayn shvester, redt opet mit eyne

00:04:23.123 --> 00:04:25.584
"kh'vel dir morgn brengen a vant zeyger"

00:04:25.590 --> 00:04:27.997
zi hot gehat a zeyger oyfn vant

00:04:29.050 --> 00:04:31.181
a sheynem zeyger a faynem

00:04:31.181 --> 00:04:33.364
zogt zi "kh'vel dir brengen bulves."

00:04:33.741 --> 00:04:36.536
m'iz gekumen tsu geyn, ikh mit di shvester

00:04:36.542 --> 00:04:38.720
un mir trogn ir avek dem zeyger mit

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:43.080
rukt arunter dem zeyger, un zi rukt arunter di bulves. me kumt tsu geyn in shtub

00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:46.360
pitsinke bulvelekh kleyninke. opgenart, ye?

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:48.653
gegebn a bisl bulves.?

00:04:48.878 --> 00:04:51.859
ober vos zol men ton? me da- me darf dokh lebn.

00:04:52.067 --> 00:04:57.444
un di kinder, az eyn mol gey ikh, ikh veys nit fun vanet ikh bin gegangen

00:04:57.501 --> 00:04:59.908
ye, az ikh hob gearbet oyfn erodrom

00:05:00.252 --> 00:05:03.531
iz geven oyfn erodrom iz geven erter

00:05:03.531 --> 00:05:06.253
vos iz geven nit vayt a dorf

00:05:06.512 --> 00:05:09.361
iz flegt men zikh arunterkhapn dortn in dorf

00:05:09.361 --> 00:05:10.843
un me flegt oysbaytn.

00:05:10.849 --> 00:05:13.279
kh'hob eyn mol oysgeton a CHATSAIT

00:05:13.279 --> 00:05:14.699
kh'bin gegangen mit a mantl

00:05:14.699 --> 00:05:16.069
kh'hob im oysgeton

00:05:16.069 --> 00:05:19.690
kedey vos zi volt mir gegebn a bisl mel far dos, un ikh bin gekumen in shtub

00:05:19.690 --> 00:05:21.510
hot men nor ⟨GESAGT⟩ az ikh bin

00:05:21.510 --> 00:05:25.367
o- okh- o- on UNK eyn mantl

00:05:25.367 --> 00:05:26.354
vos ikh hob in ⟨im⟩

00:05:26.354 --> 00:05:27.712
a- un eyn mol

00:05:27.712 --> 00:05:29.979
hob ikh oykhet a bisl mel

00:05:31.150 --> 00:05:33.080
ober di yidishe

00:05:33.080 --> 00:05:36.620
baym toyer zaynen geven azelkhene hint

00:05:37.427 --> 00:05:40.003
me tor nit reydn, ober zaynen geven

00:05:40.043 --> 00:05:43.440
zey hobn gemeynt mistome az zey veln blaybn di oysderveylte.

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:44.171
ye

00:05:45.105 --> 00:05:48.372
ikh hob gehat a bisele mel bahaltn in boykh

00:05:48.784 --> 00:05:50.482
hot er mir dertapt.

00:05:50.691 --> 00:05:54.409
"gib avek, vos hostu do dort? vos hostu do dort? gib avek."

00:05:54.409 --> 00:05:56.332
hot tsugenumen di bisl mel fun mir.

00:05:56.332 --> 00:05:59.156
vos ⟨m'vet⟩ vayter dos oysesn mit tsores, mit

00:05:59.348 --> 00:06:00.304
mit

00:06:00.917 --> 00:06:05.197
mit, mit ag- mit dos, mit moyser nefesh

00:06:05.794 --> 00:06:09.242
un az ikh hob ge- mir hobn gearbet in UNK vu mir hobn gearbet

00:06:09.242 --> 00:06:11.238
iz geven nit vayt oykh a dorf

00:06:11.245 --> 00:06:13.078
fleg ikh un nokh eyne

00:06:13.287 --> 00:06:17.717
flegn, mit a, oykhet fun, flegn mir geyn nokh der arbet

00:06:17.717 --> 00:06:19.477
flegn mir geyn in dorf

00:06:19.477 --> 00:06:21.448
un flegn oysbaytn

00:06:21.927 --> 00:06:25.633
flegt avekgebn vos nit iz, flegt men krign vos nit iz

00:06:26.078 --> 00:06:27.399
fun produktn

00:06:27.399 --> 00:06:28.079
ye?

00:06:29.740 --> 00:06:34.526
iz a bisl mel, iz ikh veys vos, zey flegn dortn vos gebn, ye

00:06:34.684 --> 00:06:35.580
far a

00:06:35.274 --> 00:06:37.134
kh'vil dir fregn a SHEELA

00:06:39.578 --> 00:06:42.290
dos vos me makht haynt, di KALETET

00:06:43.016 --> 00:06:45.336
dos vet blaybn oyf a sakh a sakh yorn

00:06:46.128 --> 00:06:50.318
vos vilstu zogn far di yunge mentshn, far di yu-, far di yugnt?

00:06:50.867 --> 00:06:52.619
ot dos vos ikh hob iberlebt

00:06:52.619 --> 00:06:54.253
dos vel ikh alts dertseyln

00:06:54.327 --> 00:06:56.649
afile mayn eynikl hob ikh oykh dertseylt.

00:06:57.263 --> 00:06:59.160
ye, ober v- vos vilstu

00:06:59.160 --> 00:07:02.325
oyf, oyf dem SOF HASIPUR, vos vilstu zogn epes

00:07:02.325 --> 00:07:03.515
a

00:07:04.603 --> 00:07:07.162
kh'vil zogn az s'iz geven di, a milkhome

00:07:07.506 --> 00:07:10.740
un di daytshn hobn, hobn umgebrakht di yidn.

00:07:12.346 --> 00:07:14.726
vos far a lekekh iz fun dem

00:07:15.756 --> 00:07:17.526
vos ken zayn a

00:07:17.526 --> 00:07:19.636
a PITARON fun dem

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:21.676
a PITARON. oyf ken eyn yidishe fus

00:07:21.676 --> 00:07:24.236
tor nit zayn oyf di daytshishe erd.

00:07:30.692 --> 00:07:33.099
vilst epes zogn far Erets Yisroel?

00:07:36.210 --> 00:07:37.571
Erets Yisroel?

00:07:38.252 --> 00:07:39.649
iz a glik

00:07:39.649 --> 00:07:41.435
az mir hobn a land

00:07:41.745 --> 00:07:44.388
a glik az mir hobn a medine

00:07:44.766 --> 00:07:47.308
un ven mir, ven mir hobn a medine

00:07:47.837 --> 00:07:49.552
far Hitlern

00:07:49.761 --> 00:07:51.527
volt aza min

00:07:52.039 --> 00:07:56.285
milkhome nit geven. me volt azoy fil nit oy- umgebrakht di yidn.

00:07:57.152 --> 00:07:59.576
der eyn eyntsiker glik iz

00:07:59.717 --> 00:08:01.533
vos mir hobn a medine.

00:08:04.797 --> 00:08:05.989
TODA RABA

00:08:06.265 --> 00:08:08.267
TODA RABA, GVERET AMDURSKI.

00:08:06.298 --> 00:08:07.017
ye.

00:08:13.285 --> 00:08:15.473
di ershte, dos bin ikh.

00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:18.881
di tsveyte, dos iz mayn shvester Nekhame.

00:08:19.090 --> 00:08:21.463
dortn iz mayn bruder Berl.

00:08:22.448 --> 00:08:25.311
lebn Berl iz mayn shvester Khaye.

00:08:25.452 --> 00:08:26.880
di mame iz

00:08:27.308 --> 00:08:29.057
di mame zitst

00:08:29.232 --> 00:08:32.010
un lebn di mame zitst der bruder Yosef.

00:08:38.073 --> 00:08:40.952
dos iz mayn shvester Nekhame.

00:08:41.179 --> 00:08:43.302
dos iz der yingele irer

00:08:43.302 --> 00:08:44.500
Nokhele

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:46.400
un di meydele Libele

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:48.140
ober in geto

00:08:48.140 --> 00:08:50.330
iz zaynen zey shoyn geven eltere.

00:08:50.330 --> 00:08:54.410
di meydele iz geven zibn yor, un der yingele iz shoyn geven tsvelf yor.

00:08:54.702 --> 00:08:57.182
vi iz gekumen tsu dir di bilder?

00:08:57.092 --> 00:09:02.098
di bilder hot a goy mir gegebn in m- un in undzer shtetl

00:09:02.307 --> 00:09:04.207
hot a goy oysgehit

00:09:04.207 --> 00:09:08.287
un er hot dos undz geda- geda- gegebn. az mir zaynen geven in Kruki

00:09:08.287 --> 00:09:10.337
hot er undz opgegebn di bilder.

00:09:15.047 --> 00:09:17.336
dos iz shoyn do in land.

00:09:18.777 --> 00:09:21.369
do in land beshas s'iz geven

00:09:22.911 --> 00:09:28.760
geven a, a BRIT MILA bay, bay dem zun dem eltern

00:09:29.003 --> 00:09:30.856
GIL, dem kleyninkn

00:09:30.856 --> 00:09:33.570
hobn mir zikh ale dortn opgefotografirt.

00:09:33.711 --> 00:09:35.581
dos iz der ershter

00:09:35.581 --> 00:09:37.699
iz mayn man Shmuel

00:09:37.699 --> 00:09:39.599
di tsveyte bin ikh

00:09:39.599 --> 00:09:43.909
der mitlster iz mayn bruder, zikhroyne LIVRACHA

00:09:43.909 --> 00:09:46.449
un di shvester un der shvoger

00:09:46.449 --> 00:09:50.070
zey zaynen shoyn nito. di dray, zey zaynen shoyn

00:09:51.227 --> 00:09:52.250
nito.

00:09:55.699 --> 00:09:59.169
dos iz mayn zun, der ershter iz mayn zun MORRIS

00:10:00.694 --> 00:10:02.341
der zun zayner

00:10:02.820 --> 00:10:03.793
TAL

00:10:04.508 --> 00:10:07.036
di KALATI, di shnur

00:10:07.036 --> 00:10:08.856
Miryem

00:10:09.047 --> 00:10:12.213
un der kleyninker yingele GIL.

00:10:12.287 --> 00:10:13.597
vu lebn zey?

00:10:13.637 --> 00:10:15.102
in CANADA.

00:10:15.102 --> 00:10:18.632
zey lebn beyde in CANADA

00:10:18.632 --> 00:10:22.262
iz gemakht gevorn shoyn mit etlekhe yor tsurik.

00:10:22.277 --> 00:10:24.346
ersht iz shoyn der yingele

00:10:24.775 --> 00:10:26.912
der yingl fuftsn yor

00:10:26.918 --> 00:10:29.800
un der tsveyter, der kleyner

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:33.140
vert er vern tsvelf yor, er, vet er vern, der groyser

00:10:33.140 --> 00:10:36.070
zekhtsn yor, un der klenerer vet er vern

00:10:36.070 --> 00:10:37.180
tsvelf yor.

00:10:41.700 --> 00:10:42.959
ZE IMA

00:10:43.506 --> 00:10:45.103
ZE IMA SHELI

00:10:45.497 --> 00:10:46.467
SHEM?

00:10:47.033 --> 00:10:48.495
SHEM SARA

00:10:48.838 --> 00:10:49.979
KORIM LO.

00:10:55.437 --> 00:10:57.053
dos iz mayn tate

00:10:57.053 --> 00:11:00.307
MORD- MORDECHAI ruft men im, Motl, MORDECHAI.

00:11:00.508 --> 00:11:01.258
GERTNER

00:11:01.140 --> 00:11:02.197
GERTNER

00:11:06.085 --> 00:11:08.273
ds iz mayn zun MORRIS

00:11:08.616 --> 00:11:10.770
un di KALATI DINA

00:11:12.270 --> 00:11:13.810
UNK Miryem iz dortn.

00:11:14.418 --> 00:11:15.647
ah, Miryem.

00:11:15.822 --> 00:11:17.402
kh'hob gemeynt az s'iz DINA.

00:11:19.551 --> 00:11:20.349
ZE

00:11:20.349 --> 00:11:21.232
TAL

00:11:21.745 --> 00:11:25.266
HAGADOL ZE TAL. ⟨HAKATANTSHIK⟩ ZE GIL.

00:11:38.940 --> 00:11:40.959
aha, aha, TOV.

00:11:41.387 --> 00:11:43.237
nu, EFSHAR?

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:43.870
EFSHAR, KEN, KEN BEVAKASHA

00:11:43.902 --> 00:11:45.414
dos iz mayn man

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:49.649
vos ikh hob im gekent a mol fun far der milkhome nokh

00:11:50.128 --> 00:11:53.547
un nokh di milkhome hobn mir zikh beyde vider getrofn.

00:11:53.622 --> 00:11:59.100
mir hobn beyde khasene gehat, un mir lebn zikh azoy beyde gliklekh, beyde tsuzamen.

00:12:00.571 --> 00:12:02.393
eyn un fuftsik yor

00:12:02.393 --> 00:12:03.971
un halevay

00:12:03.971 --> 00:12:06.086
oyf vayter nit erger.
